    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for dpkg, update-alternatives</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">dpkg and update-alternatives were updated to 1.16.16 to fix one security issue and severan non-security bugs.

The following vulnerabilities were fixed:

* CVE-2015-0840: Specially crafted deb packages could have been used to bypass source package integrity verification in local installs (boo#926749)

Also contains a number of upstream bugs and improvements.
</Note>
